  "dn7:4.3": "‘The soul and the body are the same thing’ or ‘The soul and the body are different things’?” ",
  "dn7:4.4": "“It would, reverend.” ",
  "dn7:4.5": "",
  "dn7:4.6": "“But reverends, I know and see like this. ",
